<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans d. J. von Giech</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Göldlein, Diener der Stadt, wegen des Angriffs des Adressaten an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_589" id="293v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_589_r1l20">eydem </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_589_r1l21">VVir ſenden cʒu euch Hanſen Göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dẏener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_589_r1l22">mit euch ʒu reden als von des cʒugriffs wegen / den Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_589_r1l23"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> getan habt / dabey etliche dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_589_r1l24">als vns geſagt iſt / Vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> vt in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_589" id="293v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Eydem</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir senden czu euch Hansen Göldlein,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener, mit euch zu
                                                reden als von des czugriffs wegen, den ir
                                                  <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> getan habt,
                                                dabey etliche die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                                                auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als uns gesagt
                                                ist. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> ut in
                                                  <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
